    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Collaborate with the Data Science team to identify and implement two new data drift detection algorithms. Ensure their outputs are logged and metrics are available for monitoring.</p>

<p>Note. only and only 2 of those that are either more critical or easier to implement.</p>

<p>Note must be tested and confirmed by DS using Aura QA 1</p>

<p>Must have severity level</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
