        <tr id="comment-body-263120"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p><b>Notes from Sprint planning:</b></p>

<ol>
	<li>Only going to address 2 more data drift scenarios<br/>
<a href="https://mikmakai.atlassian.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?accountId=712020%3A6dd63376-8785-4213-9a08-216ba28731c0" class="user-hover" rel="712020:6dd63376-8785-4213-9a08-216ba28731c0" data-account-id="712020:6dd63376-8785-4213-9a08-216ba28731c0" accountid="712020:6dd63376-8785-4213-9a08-216ba28731c0" rel="noreferrer">seema.dhamija</a> Pls help identify these scenarios and add those to the ticket as comments. </li>
	<li>Reduced SP to 2 as per Seyed’s suggestions.</li>
</ol>

        </td></tr>
                <tr id="comment-header-264459"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            Comment by  
                                                    
                
        
            <a class="user-hover" rel="712020:015c74e4-5e56-4f7c-838a-9a5b2cde16fc"
